    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable daily driver for someone looking for value over aesthetics. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and a few small dings consistent with its age, and the paint has begun to fade on the roof. Inside, the upholstery shows significant wear and some staining, though all major electronics and the air conditioning remain functional. Mechanically, it runs and drives well, though it will likely need new tires and a brake service in the near future. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that has been used regularly and priced according to its current state.",
