    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver for anyone looking for reliable transportation on a budget. The engine starts up consistently and the transmission shifts through all gears, though you may notice a slight hesitation during cold starts. Visually, the car shows its age with some noticeable scratches on the passenger side doors and fading paint on the hood. The interior is clean but has some wear on the driver's seat upholstery and a non-functioning radio volume knob. It's a solid car that has been maintained mechanically, even if it isn't perfect to look at.",
