    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Get ready for a fantastic ride! This car is in good, solid condition and has been well-maintained to ensure it's ready for its next owner. It runs smoothly and looks great, showing only the typical signs of careful use you'd expect from a reliable pre-owned vehicle. If you're looking for a dependable, high-quality car that strikes the perfect balance between performance and value, this is the one for you!",
