    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "Check out this dependable ride that's perfect for someone looking for a solid value! This car is in fair condition, meaning it's seen some honest use and has a bit of character, but it's still ready to get you where you need to go. It\u2019s a great choice for a daily driver that you won't have to baby. Come take a look and see if this reliable workhorse is the right fit for your needs!",
