      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm looking to find a new home for this awesome ride. It\u2019s been super reliable for me and is still in really solid shape, perfect for someone who wants a dependable car without the brand-new price tag. It runs great, looks sharp, and has plenty of life left in it! I\u2019ve taken good care of it, and I'd love for you to come by, take it for a spin, and see for yourself. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'm super happy to chat!",
