    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54B32 3.2L inline-six. This unit boasts individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing, delivering a linear power band up to its 7,900 RPM redline through a precise Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox. The chassis has undergone critical subframe reinforcement, and cam gear bolts have been addressed to ensure long-term structural and mechanical durability. Equipped with a variable M Differential Lock and factory-tuned MacPherson strut front/multi-link rear suspension, the handling remains sharp and communicative. The vehicle presents in honest condition with minor aesthetic patina consistent with its age, but the drivetrain remains tight and responsive. This is a robust, driver-spec example of BMW's peak analog engineering.",
